r podcasts. Target audience: teens and young adults. Audiobook feature upcoming.\",\n                    \"placeholder\": \"Explain briefly the product is, or which features to focus\",\n                    \"required\": false\n                }\n            ],\n            \"categories\": {},\n            \"unsupportedLanguages\": []\n        },\n        \"bullet-point-to-answers\": {\n            \"title\": \"Bullet Point to Answers\",\n            \"templateSlug\": \"bullet-point-to-answers\",\n            \"description\": \"Get bulleted lists of answers to related questions while writing long-form content\",\n            \"inputFields\": [\n                {\n                    \"label\": \"Question\",\n                    \"name\": \"question\",\n                    \"sample\": \"What is depreciation in economics?\",\n                    \"placeholder\": \"Enter the question to get an answer in bullet points\",\n                    \"required\": true\n                },\n                {\n                    \"label\": \"Additional Instruction\",\n                    \"name\": \"additionalInstruction\",\n                    \"sample\": \"define the term in detail and multiple bullet points\",\n                    \"placeholder\": \"You can give instruction/context for a more accurate output (optional)\",\n                    \"required\": false\n                }\n            ],\n            \"categories\": {},\n            \"unsupportedLanguages\": []\n        },\n        \"explain-why\": {\n            \"title\": \"Explain Why\",\n            \"templateSlug\": \"explain-why\",\n            \"description\": \"Questions need answering and concepts need explaining — let’s explain why\",\n            \"inputFields\": [\n                {\n                    \"label\": \"Question\",\n                    \"name\": \"question\",\n                    \"sample\": \"Why do we use chi square test?\",\n                    \"placeholder\": \"Enter a WH-type question that you need explained\",\n                    \"required\": true\n                },\n                {\n                    \"label\": \"Context\",\n                    \"name\": \"context\",\n                    \"sample\": \"explain in multiple sentences the use cases of chi square test and how it comes of use\",\n                    \"placeholder\": \"You can give additional instruction/context for a more accurate output (optional)\",\n                    \"required\": false\n                }\n            ],\n            \"categories\": {},\n            \"unsupportedLanguages\": []\n        },\n        \"feature-benefit\": {\n            \"title\": \"Feature - Benefit\",\n            \"templateSlug\": \"feature-benefit\",\n            \"description\": \"Describe what your product/service does and get the detailed benefits in return\",\n            \"inputFields\": [\n                {\n                    \"label\": \"Product name\",\n                    \"name\": \"productName\",\n                    \"sample\": \"Tumblr\",\n                    \"placeholder\": \"Enter the product name\",\n                    \"required\": true\n                },\n                {\n                    \"label\": \"Product description\",\n                    \"name\": \"productDescription\",\n                    \"sample\": \"Tumblr is a microblogging and social networking site that allows users to create an online diary or blog. Users can follow their favorite interests, other Tumblrs, and brand influencers to share content to and from. You can reblog posts, photos or videos that you like and share on your blog for your followers to see. Tumblr was relatively popular among tweens and teens in its heyday, circa 2013.\",\n                    \"placeholder\": \"Enter the product\'s features here to generate its benefits\",\n                    \"required\": true\n                }\n            ],\n            \"categories\": {},\n            \"unsupportedLanguages\": []\n      