ent warranty, worldwide free shipping\",\n                    \"placeholder\": \"Specify the keywords/key phrases for the product long description\",\n                    \"required\": true\n                }\n            ],\n            \"categories\": {},\n            \"unsupportedLanguages\": []\n        },\n        \"pros-and-cons\": {\n            \"title\": \"Pros and Cons\",\n            \"templateSlug\": \"pros-and-cons\",\n            \"description\": \"Generate a list of pros and cons about any given topic to utilize in your content\",\n            \"inputFields\": [\n                {\n                    \"label\": \"Topic\",\n                    \"name\": \"topic\",\n                    \"sample\": \"Modern medicine\",\n                    \"placeholder\": \"Enter a topic to get the pros and cons of it\",\n                    \"required\": true\n                },\n                {\n                    \"label\": \"Context/Additional Instruction\",\n                    \"name\": \"context/additionalInstruction\",\n                    \"sample\": \"write the pros and cons of consuming/using modern medicine\",\n                    \"placeholder\": \"You can give additional instruction/context for a more accurate output (optional)\",\n                    \"required\": false\n                }\n            ],\n            \"categories\": {},\n            \"unsupportedLanguages\": []\n        },\n        \"woocommerce-product-title\": {\n            \"title\": \"WooCommerce Product Title\",\n            \"templateSlug\": \"woocommerce-product-title\",\n            \"description\": \"Generate keyword-optimized product titles to rank & convert with your WooCommerce website\",\n            \"inputFields\": [\n                {\n                    \"label\": \"Product name\",\n                    \"name\": \"productName\",\n                    \"sample\": \"Kellogg\'s Corn Flakes with Real Strawberry Puree\",\n                    \"placeholder\": \"Enter the product name\",\n                    \"required\": true\n                },\n                {\n                    \"label\": \"Keywords\",\n                    \"name\": \"keywords\",\n                    \"sample\": \"breakfast cereal, vitamin c, low-fat, cholesterol free, 300 grams\",\n                    \"placeholder\": \"Specify which keywords should the product title be based on\",\n                    \"required\": true\n                }\n            ],\n            \"categories\": {},\n            \"unsupportedLanguages\": []\n        },\n        \"woocommerce-product-short-description\": {\n            \"title\": \"WooCommerce Product Short Description\",\n            \"templateSlug\": \"woocommerce-product-short-description\",\n            \"description\": \"Get short descriptions/excerpts for your WooCommerce products optimized for your desired keywords\",\n            \"inputFields\": [\n                {\n                    \"label\": \"Product name\",\n                    \"name\": \"productName\",\n                    \"sample\": \"Garantia Stone 2 in1 Water Tank\",\n                    \"placeholder\": \"Enter the product name\",\n                    \"required\": true\n                },\n                {\n                    \"label\": \"Keywords\",\n                    \"name\": \"keywords\",\n                    \"sample\": \"water tank, 2 in 1, harvest rainwater, water butt, planter cup on top, integrated thread\",\n                    \"placeholder\": \"Specify which keywords should the product short description be based on\",\n                    \"required\": true\n                }\n            ],\n            \"categories\": {},\n            \"unsupportedLanguages\": []\n        },\n        \"taglines\": {\n            \"title\": \"Taglines\",\n            \"templateSlug\": \"taglines\",\n            \"description\": \"Get genie to write taglines for your brands, products, services, or any content\",\n            \"inputFields\": [\n   